<p>
	This fantastic snowman decoration is great for bringing that Christmas feel to any house. It would make a great addition as a Christmas decoration as it truly does look brilliant. This fluffy snowman has a beany body so can easily stand anywhere on its own, and it could also be used as a door stop for a light door. The snowman has two bell buttons down his front, twig like arms and is wearing a scarf and a lovely warm bobble hat on his head. The snowman has a big smile on his face with two beady eyes, a long pointy nose and pink flushed cheeks. The snowman stands at 26cm tall.</p>
